31:05.250 --> 31:06.416
Whoa!

31:10.000 --> 31:12.583
How on earth do you get reception up here?

31:14.250 --> 31:15.791
Couple of good satellite dishes out front

31:15.875 --> 31:18.541
will get you anything within about
400 million light-years.

