Hi, honey.

31:19.708 --> 31:20.750
KYRA: Are you at the house?

31:20.833 --> 31:23.916
Yeah, no, (STAMMERS)
I'm just with some friends.

31:24.458 --> 31:26.958
Oh, okay. Well, what time
do you think you'll be home?

31:29.708 --> 31:33.708
Hey, would it be okay
if I'm just a little bit late?

31:35.125 --> 31:39.958
